text: "Work It" is a song by American rapper Nelly featuring singer Justin Timberlake. It was the fifth single from Nelly's second album Nellyville. The song was released on February 25, 2003. The song reached number 7 on the UK Singles Chart and 68 on the U.S. Billboard Hot 100. Category:Nelly songs Category:2003 songs
title: Work It
